creator: Cryptocurrencyapplication
descriptionHtml:
This is Blockchain Cryptocurrency Application with Crypto Currency Rate Widget and Cryptocurrencies Portfolio, which can be used as crypto currency tracker for Bitcoin price, Ethereum price, Ripple price and Altcoin prices.

Keep track of the blockchain crypto currencies rates, get analitycs of coinmarketcap using brand new cryptocurrency widget. Learn Bitcoin portfolio, watch for crypto currency exchange rate and keep up to date with the latest Cryptocurrencies News.

Also at your disposal is usable cryptocurrency converter, in which you can ccompare bitcoin price to altcoin price and other cryptocurrencies.

Another functional feature is cryptocurrency calculator, which allows you to count the profit from operations with crypto currency exchange.

The rates of coins is provided from coinmarketcap site.

MORE FEATURES

✓ Sorting of cryptocurrencies list by rank, price, capitalization, etc.
✓ Favorites - List of favorite coins.
✓ Coin price alert — possibility to get immediate notifications when bitcoin or other cryptocoin grows/drops to a certain point.
✓ Market Capitalizations from coinmarketcap site.
✓ Bitcoin price widget / Altcoin price widget - simple widget for tracking crypto coins rate.
✓ Cryptoсurrency portfolio – allows to add any of blockchain coins to your portfolio and track all the changes favorite cryptocurrencies.
✓Cryptocurrencies converter - allows convert any cryptocurrency to USD, EUR, RUB and vice versa.
✓Api import from Exmo

If you have any suggestion or you see some data is wrong or some charts is not loaded please write us, we try quickly fix it.

descriptionHtml:
This is Blockchain Cryptocurrency Application with Crypto Currency Rate Widget and Cryptocurrencies Portfolio, which can be used as crypto currency tracker for Bitcoin price, Ethereum price, Ripple price and Altcoin prices.

Keep track of the blockchain crypto currencies rates, get analitycs of coinmarketcap using brand new cryptocurrency widget. Learn Bitcoin portfolio, watch for crypto currency exchange rate and keep up to date with the latest Cryptocurrencies News.

Also at your disposal is usable cryptocurrency converter, in which you can ccompare bitcoin price to altcoin price and other cryptocurrencies.

Another functional feature is cryptocurrency calculator, which allows you to count the profit from operations with crypto currency exchange.

The rates of coins is provided from coinmarketcap site.

MORE FEATURES

✓ Sorting of cryptocurrencies list by rank, price, capitalization, etc.
✓ Favorites - List of favorite coins.
✓ Coin price alert — possibility to get immediate notifications when bitcoin or other cryptocoin grows/drops to a certain point.
✓ Market Capitalizations from coinmarketcap site.
✓ Bitcoin price widget / Altcoin price widget - simple widget for tracking crypto coins rate.
✓ Cryptoсurrency portfolio – allows to add any of blockchain coins to your portfolio and track all the changes favorite cryptocurrencies.
✓Cryptocurrencies converter - allows convert any cryptocurrency to USD, EUR, RUB and vice versa.
✓Api import from Exmo

If you have any suggestion or you see some data is wrong or some charts is not loaded please write us, we try quickly fix it.
